DOCUMENT();        # This should be the first executable line in the problem.

loadMacros(
  "PGstandard.pl",
  "PGchoicemacros.pl",
  "PGcourse.pl"
);

TEXT(beginproblem());
$showPartialCorrectAnswers = 1;

$a1 = random(2,5,1);
$b1 = random(2,10,1);
$c1 = random(1,4,1);
$d1 = sqrt($b1*$b1+4*$a1*$c1);

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
The equation \($a1 x^4-$b1 x^3 - $c1 x^2 = 0\) has three real solutions \(A\), \(B\), and \(C\)
where \(A < B < C\)  $BR and \(A\) is:
\{ans_rule(25) \}
$BR
EOT

$ans = ($b1-$d1)/(2*$a1);
ANS(num_cmp($ans));

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
and \(B\) is:
\{ans_rule(25) \}
$BR
EOT

$ans = 0;
ANS(num_cmp($ans));

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
and \(C\) is:
\{ans_rule(25) \}
$BR
EOT

$ans = ($b1+$d1)/(2*$a1);
ANS(num_cmp($ans));

ENDDOCUMENT();        # This should be the last executable line in the problem.
